name: Borzoi Coin
description: Borzoi Coin ($BORZOI) is a community-driven meme token on the Ethereum network, inspired by the 'let me do it for you' meme featuring the distinctive Borzoi dog breed. Celebrated for its comically long nose, elongated body, and playful demeanor, Borzois rose to insane virality after memes depicted Borzoi's long nose extending out and doing random things.
